version_description: V3.1 incorporates fixes to optimise performance and user experience. We have introduced a "Feature Launcher" for faster access to Bank, Dine, Apple Pay, Apply, Deals and Travel. With this version, navigation has also been optimised for dine so that you can easily search on where to dine at.

V4.0.1 incorporates fixes to optimise performance and user experience.
We have also optimise the design for dine to make leaving a restaurant review simpler and more intuitive. With this version, search has also been optimised for dine so that you can easily search on where to dine at.
V4.1.0 incorporates fixes to optimise performance and security.
V4.1.1 incorporates fixes to optimise performance.

V4.2 introduces new features like Mighty Secure, Call my Advisor and Rewards.

Mighty Secure is a new convenient and secure way to access your accounts and authorise transactions.
Call my Advisor allows Privilege, Privilege Reserve, Wealth and Private banking customers to quickly contact their Advisors.
Rewards allow credit card customers to easily redeem their rewards on the go.
